description:
AJKB-03 EMBROIDERED NET 3 PCS

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Peshwas: Net Trouser: Silk Dupatta: Net Color: Pink

Echoing the charm of a rose garden, this ensemble redefines feminine grace. The embroidered Peshwas, a blooming work of art, is delicately adorned with light gold zari weaving through soft tea pink, lilac, and beige threads. Sparkling accents of light gold 3mm cupped sequins are artfully dispersed across the outfit, while 9mm sequins illuminate the borders and bodice, enhancing its beauty. Paired with an embroidered dupatta, a gentle breath of elegance, this ensemble is a vision of pure perfection.
DESIGN DETAILS:

Embroidered front bodice on net
Embroidered back bodice on net
1.5 meter embroidered border for front & back neckline on net
22 embroidered Kalis for peshwas on net
5 meter embroidered border for ghera on net
Pair of embroidered sleeves on net
2.5 meter embroidered dupatta with 4-side border on net
1.5 meter wide-width silk for trouser
